citations:
  citation-awoiaf-alleras:
    source: source-awoiaf
    properties:
      locator: "Alleras"
      accessed: "2026-03-15"
    notes: "Dornish culture. Born in Dorne. Alias: the Sphinx. Title: Acolyte at the Citadel. Half-Dornish, half-Summer Islander. Allegiance: Citadel. Father is a Dornishman, mother a Summer Islander trader. Has forged three links in his maester's chain. Widely believed to be Sarella Sand, bastard daughter of Oberyn Martell, in disguise."
